    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a pencil-sketched character and journey through hand-drawn levels in this story-based platformer. Explore sketches, paintings, and diary entries to reveal the story of one ordinary man’s life through the 80s, 90s, 00s and up to the modern era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/8e176d86f408c744407a167c36f7b0a2.poster.avif?t=1771772952\" width=570 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/8e176d86f408c744407a167c36f7b0a2.webm?t=1771772952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/8e176d86f408c744407a167c36f7b0a2.mp4?t=1771772952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A narrative-based, single player adventure with a focus on environmental variety, story, and challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and intuitive controls - move, jump, dash, and a few other surprises here and there.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular checkpoints throughout areas, with instant respawns. Game saves at the start of each new level.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/d2ab8c24febc9e869888b7fa04556ffc.poster.avif?t=1771772952\" width=756 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/d2ab8c24febc9e869888b7fa04556ffc.webm?t=1771772952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/d2ab8c24febc9e869888b7fa04556ffc.mp4?t=1771772952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zero skill-trees, unlockables, or purchasable items. Just raw, honest platforming (with the occasional power up of course).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original music, composed with care for each level of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
